{"tid":2524787,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖][一年長途遊記] 中南美到南極-西伯利亞至東歐 (完)","createTime":"2021-05-10T18:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T20:16:31.000Z","uid":161156,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c73e6d7f9f8b10db0cf3810664f28b861e3c5cf","tid":2524787,"uid":161156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"<strong>上回提要</strong><br />\n墨西哥<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPLvs2yoUmV4nCY8R5zZx4KcYtDgLMtZBmUBMYaWKybSD?filename=GoJZczn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGoJZczn.jpg&h=82307802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY1Y7hnsKuZzFU5VLHj72akHZhATbDcER9pJw2pnDn1hZ?filename=2bFwOf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2bFwOf9.jpg&h=a3a4e2e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYZjTPokJc1GU57g3jahmGwqTnfdEuEpPopGDdDTVWgPE?filename=tWaAvzG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWaAvzG.jpg&h=cb372887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伯利茲<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZCoNwbi2FHNTGmtteW4Z2cMxc75gxEpZ7dFZzYYjCjoW?filename=MUed1s4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUed1s4.jpg&h=a83c0223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n危地馬拉<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbsrYjdGNUr23FwSacHkU6uMa3JsanKN99ZYVCn8x4YjE?filename=T1HnU1O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1HnU1O.jpg&h=13f1f118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZERdGZV2BDHPuN3nSJMd584UBgcZmJ1NCxhhRdxg2eHq?filename=CV2y1ta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCV2y1ta.jpg&h=8a4b9149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哥斯達黎加<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWYGBndz7JfvJbtfiaNtoxAinwnienNJi8QqBS6pnBjXN?filename=4e7WeOp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4e7WeOp.jpg&h=5f999364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南極<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUMKKyWXtYqavV2N4565Caewr1YFkwPwcBpPFFiTiaF29?filename=b7yBZhQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7yBZhQ.jpg&h=a5c1c905&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSN1bRwLeabQQ7EL4zffWYgv64h5yaw28RVRHeDqHCHNt?filename=CVggeRo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCVggeRo.jpg&h=868d9cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdUEHnaHPJUSCHFB9kb2UkD19GAtWVDFW21Lw576pwCj9?filename=nCPYtbr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnCPYtbr.jpg&h=4e753094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿根廷<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdbbMo3wwEzdFqtuTsRCBhevVgUqkb1EorV4AGhgJQQku?filename=HkrLSNn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHkrLSNn.jpg&h=5b55fbf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNdvwEYJcksbUnVNtbry6nBN7VGi17LfncHmc8DYEqtTB?filename=1WTa3KP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1WTa3KP.jpg&h=339c5f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n智利<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQQByZXkRXFuAxc7wYfrWKevapS5L3xoWivV2fQaFiHze?filename=K4VAvqn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK4VAvqn.jpg&h=8191567e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX7jLLRxrQFMxbR6ms6Ldjy7hHGMvDUwf993QUhaCfvcH?filename=ruXrB4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FruXrB4d.jpg&h=d86e2365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n玻利維亞<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPYeC61thupXxaYHFKgYQeTE68SAB4znUmYyJJpT27JbM?filename=xAXjcDq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxAXjcDq.jpg&h=bdcbcfbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYQCaZnJF6zUShj1oYGHpzuYZ2a1zPUxfWGgtiznzkx5Y?filename=iO27mva.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiO27mva.jpg&h=af6ae391&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n秘魯<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaY3xQPfWgFAZqZ5VM5EoVNhQGSgcwemXYmQDD4Gp8U4Q?filename=zPrzL3i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzPrzL3i.jpg&h=ec0e5fc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZk7wkxJJppHYnRwAPpMb6dXADtkamCpDwHGVojTmVaSv?filename=Zdq48cW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZdq48cW.jpg&h=08bd6561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVwkowGtsKtmD5EwR2XSAe2vWGshojgKH96BX1xBsvdbX?filename=nVHvjkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVHvjkd.jpg&h=d73dfae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒙古<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP2JmFDJnkv8gBr2pFeuZTdogv2NZ5ucSM45b2PQceiaq?filename=Ls4tQtR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLs4tQtR.jpg&h=8c826550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUuuFzgjE3oTevBH9bYGu4EN74qXCXG6BjsCeMXz4pA7m?filename=yZFs57X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZFs57X.jpg&h=d885837c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPmnLDKxWbT2pg3fFLSKpqdNJCYyzJ95q5HGB5gwT5Mhs?filename=fe3BZnn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffe3BZnn.jpg&h=2018a3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNsRraSkdjNxEkz3Gwf5YsBLJZviRUFp8G3wGRtTd6wh3?filename=axEajmV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxEajmV.jpg&h=65a1f47d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n愛沙尼亞<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWep9SCgfb9kSDaw4KPhwKQr95rs7xLWuS1BFq5ph9v1A?filename=fEK5SHx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEK5SHx.jpg&h=d113b02e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拉脫維亞<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTw33xqMwDKwtbtoaWq52wREjQsGFBYJb6UmaQbVscAtu?filename=QOOitny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQOOitny.jpg&h=c435affe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34e167ceb5ded5c1a3204e14f17330cb2b1e6e12","tid":2524787,"uid":161156,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T18:56:33.000Z","msg":"故事係咁既，事源我同男朋友27歲既時候決定裸辭，想係組織小家庭之前任性一次，揹起背囊去一場自由自在既旅行，一齊好好感受呢個世界。時間上當初定左係去一至兩年，最後係19年因為放唔低香港既事就提早腰斬左個行程返左黎，但我地從來無後悔呢個決定，因為就算外面既世界再美好，都唔係我既家。<br />\n<br />\n世界好大，有好多未知既事、唔同既文化、美麗而善良既人民，我地認識到好多朋友，亦遇上過車禍同搶劫，所有好既壞既都係一個美好既經歷。好感激我地曾經有一個咁美好既旅程，希望有朝一日可以將未行完既旅程繼續啦。<br />\n<br />\n最後整個旅程去左一年，因為我地都比較鍾意隨心而行，所以全程都無訂一個行程表，只有由北至南，東至西既一個大約概念，沿途再邊走邊問人會唔會有咩當地人先知道既有趣地方咁。而中途發生左啲意外所以返左一返香港，最後整體既路線如下:<br />\n<br />\n美國&gt;墨西哥&gt;伯利茲&gt;危地馬拉&gt;哥斯達黎加&gt;巴拿馬&gt;阿根廷&gt;南極&gt;阿根廷&gt;智利&gt;玻利維亞&gt;秘魯&gt;哥倫比亞&gt;西班牙&gt;德國&gt;法國&gt;意大利&gt;馬爾他&gt;香港&gt;北京&gt;蒙古&gt;俄羅斯&gt;芬蘭&gt;愛沙尼亞&gt;拉脫維亞&gt; <strong>[立陶宛]</strong> &gt;波蘭&gt;匈牙利&gt;塞浦路斯&gt;格魯吉亞&gt;香港<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家鍾意睇我地呢兩個平凡人既遊記，亦唔介意我會間歇性失蹤幾日繼續支持我(好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。希望大家睇完都可以知道，即使係好似我地咁樣既普通人，只要願意揹起背囊踏出去，就再無任何野可以阻止到你窺探呢個世界。當你敞開心扉去感受，最後從旅行中得到既野，將會遠超想像。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎重溫返前兩篇遊記:<br />\n<ins>美國至伯利茲篇</ins> - <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/972871/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/972871/page/1</a><br />\n<ins>危地馬拉至拉脫維亞篇</ins> - <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2156793/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2156793/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n下一站，我地要繼續向立陶宛進發喇。"},{"pid":"8a85135bca327973039d1063220e0d30180a1ee5","tid":2524787,"uid":161156,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T19:32:09.000Z","msg":"[立陶宛 &ndash; &Scaron;iauliai]<br />\n<br />\n離開拉脫維亞，我地帶住晌街市買既兩盒士多啤梨上路，出發去波羅的海三小國既最後一個國家，立陶宛北部既城市&Scaron;iauliai<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNqzeeUAr8GMgaLtpwZnmidKh7yNTTwHd4h6bN9B1bNKF?filename=VdYN6nv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVdYN6nv.jpg&h=faa2e611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三小國之間既交通時間好短，坐一至三個鐘車就可以由一個城市去到另一個城市，對比起之前晌中南美閒閒地都要搭十零廿個鐘巴士，車上面廁所成日壞，有啲又無冷氣，呢度簡直係天堂。雖然係咁，我地硬係會成日掛著係中南美旅行既日子，到底人總係犯賤丫，定係果種刺激感真係太令人上癮呢? 適應左之前果種刺激既旅行模式，原來好難返得返轉頭。<br />\n<br />\n&Scaron;iaulia最出名既景點係十字架山，時間唔夠既話可以day trip咁去完十字架山就走，但我地唔想咁趕，所以會係度住返兩晚。繼續住殘舊風apartment<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmerubF4d3d9FUhXXAyJSHAcgAuJjD1LjrvBZE6U4mW4rj?filename=J6g4pb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6g4pb4.jpg&h=208e6764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n估唔到真係有屋主會將鎖匙放係地毯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇黎呢度治安好好<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZUQMdWvfmsTELHAukcUdXH7uT8bVsg6baQZQZFGBF61M?filename=3t5AvR7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3t5AvR7.jpg&h=4bf382d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRnFMFaR23QFfwif2izSKQLn5FHP7Vc9GcE4pMcwwScPi?filename=DxaMCx0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDxaMCx0.jpg&h=f84c9947&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n屋主品味都幾獨特，我諗起將雪櫃放係洗衣機頂果個post<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPA1PEW1tGZuf4pR6E3p5J2FksCW5JSdtJmXeJEhB4B9V?filename=ik01rrA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fik01rrA.jpg&h=aa1c7f11&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n上面個乾衣機仲要放到歪歪地，開機之後部機邊fing邊搖咁，很是不安。<br />\n<br />\n呢度係立陶宛第四大既城市，感覺似係一個城市化少少既小鎮。市入面都唔係好見到遊客，我地出街隨便行下<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVTkXGRGJm9fE3f5Y1eFB963nkH1cWC27NLCj54G2HgVM?filename=R786Czw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR786Czw.jpg&h=8dbefc5b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPNjeqppE8gC4zL7GrawxjbBHjitn3EpQfZwtRHxA7Y2v?filename=9e1LS71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9e1LS71.jpg&h=41285491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到一個湖邊，瞓下草地，睇下鴨<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTmQzkPAC2oKnxcbV9xZjixJf5qhThXr2ZSZ2xah8RtDC?filename=bzTKpfe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbzTKpfe.png&h=4e14c151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖邊有個形狀成個腦咁既石陣，上網睇話呢個叫做能量迷宮，由內行去外再行返入內就可以完成一個吸收能量同治癒心靈既療程<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以我地悟性太低，行完一轉覺得無乜料到 <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd6N1sNCaU1cMoPsJEBpBpcT32nh4KovVMWSFCc9mZf2J?filename=0uGHaVF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uGHaVF.jpg&h=a15c05f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔離係一個紀念太陽既公園，中間有個小金人像，&Scaron;iauliai呢個名係由立陶宛文中既弓手變化而成，所以我地諗佢某程度上應該係代表左呢個城市<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmadbW2G9ZDgvKee9kK71CyST1VkLSQQUbXd5EyUodGZug?filename=tmbPAnz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtmbPAnz.jpg&h=8b3ca6e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返去既時候經過呢個有啲特別既公雞鐘，上網睇話佢識講多國語言歡迎遊客黎到，不過我地記錯左雞叫時間，聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX4HCLofWEbC2zzVMHmm6dNim8rkatTZsMGpWHp53mLuc?filename=SqMcx9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSqMcx9r.jpg&h=87359cb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地發現呢度啲人好鐘意食紅菜頭，而且鐘意搞到啲顏色好詭異，今日晚飯係晌超級市場不既紅菜頭沙律搭雞脾。呢度啲紅菜頭又幾好食，一啲草青味都無，仲好甜添<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUBpmTQSRvC6ksiL1A3K6knrSyydNmoydyXJGZpDjRaDv?filename=mA6gfop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmA6gfop.jpg&h=7f0ab809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立陶宛似乎仲有一道名菜，係用紅菜頭整既粉紅色凍湯，聽落好有趣，急不及待想獵奇一下了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7fd77fccc128b78a7f55c6ec2baf9ef5687354","tid":2524787,"uid":161156,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T20:21:30.000Z","msg":"休息左一日，第二日我地就出發去十字架山，由&Scaron;iauliai巴士總站搭15分鐘巴士就去到架喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZwxHKjfx4xCeVHx6nR5tpnAgqafxbn4znVMmjnfpD8uY?filename=ygQ1ry7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FygQ1ry7.jpg&h=0d89dc2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴士站有schedule拎，每個鐘都有一班車，幾方便<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdNA5t53cDyQDNuvfV7SxRs4CzPKRAcRSQxjMRnyCuGYp?filename=4qOna0U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qOna0U.jpg&h=cd211df7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢架係晌鄉村之間穿梭既普通巴士，除左我地之外所有乘客都係啲公公婆婆居民<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb6TBDV7F9yGyhEXaioSpPREsFRpdxhnXqQXEuDgcBxRW?filename=1f7bOOs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1f7bOOs.jpg&h=e93de263&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n遊客坐得呢架車都係去十字架山，所以司機同啲老人家都好好，差不多到站就會係咁提我地準備落車。落地之後唔係即刻見到十字架山，要先行半個鐘左右既路，途中經過一大片小黃花，係個陽光普照既天氣下寧舍靚，係春天既氣息呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd8aDAc6Y3BVdDMiaM1kuuMGRkkSnk8TyhpJQrjSig1w7?filename=D2o2VuH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2o2VuH.jpg&h=b4083c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT3Cu6Ve1nYrZZV7QZYhB38APXjnbjEx9HFU4soRCJjpq?filename=f05XKn3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff05XKn3.jpg&h=919612e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmdk21AN3QHah3B8bCwztejpFRWTHc9UzN5Q6zSXARgELJ?filename=O2QgZWp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO2QgZWp.jpg&h=efd291cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快我地就黎到入口位置，呢度有幾間士多，有興趣既話可以係度買啲十字架入去<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdVzPTW5tLR3Wk7dpbGTWtvFmFajduLVuWWeCgL1dZBJN?filename=oXGDtP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXGDtP7.jpg&h=fcec61f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旁邊係一間對住十字架山既教堂<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmafQbmF6hWxQp63WRNDwnq8LqqRRyZQUQC65PqTw3S9F8?filename=Mrsy2am.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMrsy2am.jpg&h=c31eb747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十字架山並唔係一座山，亦唔係墳墓或者教堂，最貼切既形容應該係一個抗爭既標誌。呢度前身係一個丘堡，由1831年開始已經有人將十字架放係度，紀念反俄既烈士。真正開始堆起十字架係直至到後來既蘇聯時期，立陶宛淪陷，信眾開始紛紛前來放低十字架。除左祈求和平，仲帶有一個更重要既訊息，立陶宛人透過呢個行為，表達即使被侵佔，但佢地仍然會忠於原來既身份、宗教信仰同傳統，係一個和平抗爭既象徵。無數既立陶宛人將十字架帶黎放晌呢度，久而久之遠望就好似一個由十字架堆成既山丘<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeVim2ufhmkuQEyYt8ytJGg775dUETFji1r9YKnjFQ9KP?filename=FqtBZYu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqtBZYu.jpg&h=b6b8c963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有極權都害怕人民團結而具民族主義，就算只係黎放低十字架，呢個彰顯民族性既行為都足以令當時既蘇聯政府畏懼，三番四次想剷除呢個地方，但每次清場過後，立陶宛人總會繼續將十字架帶黎，放低，帶黎，又再放低。立陶宛人就係靠住呢一份信念，捱過被侵佔既艱苦歲月。<br />\n<br />\n呢度每個十字架都帶住人民既信念，令十字架山彷彿有著一股好強既力量，即使無任何宗教信仰，黎到呢度都會有一種莫名既感動<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWEYJNZHNgXqMGC6WoQwT6tJAVcL1hNivpyxZzQ6gqDFC?filename=tbqppqc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftbqppqc.jpg&h=c6ea8dad&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVQBrddpy3iA2D9SyqZXRfVadaEGBUg6jF8CgGNyzYshg?filename=ReoN6Dy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FReoN6Dy.jpg&h=0b7339fa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVVffJW5D2LtrgQeJ89nK4st3Q6WZFMTpLW5r7KCiyx5a?filename=YpaQj0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYpaQj0A.jpg&h=6113481a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcFfqK3XM7u4vNpoergyAr6GCe4LmsCbMaLMztjroTSCk?filename=NwNjdh9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNwNjdh9.jpg&h=d60709c7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大十字架上掛滿小十字架<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQzEQidTxgWDtur6MEx9AdzTDzehDhtyJhcmeKbx5Ugxz?filename=Z9LHVw0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ9LHVw0.jpg&h=dc894bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倒塌既舊十字架上又插滿新既十字架<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmchNmn6FGVAmSMV9Yx4ZcwKvbmuRERsgU7M1a4gdKeCpg?filename=zMt6COh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMt6COh.jpg&h=077cdc7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n痛苦既歷史已經過去，而家新掛上既係各式各樣不同既十字架，帶住來自世界各地既祈望，現時粗略估計呢度已經有超過20萬個十字架喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfE2rtHFAXZAXwe2Hi8NGyLmaUQhdZpivBSJQjK53aK6j?filename=iMBv4rn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiMBv4rn.jpg&h=3d77ff23&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXBBFiWmAgxYYAqeT3iQiuBx1subKXLJWuKb985jvu7Pd?filename=tK60Hc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtK60Hc2.jpg&h=002cd043&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSXJtPcira5RTW7uNXSHRUHtJ4FjB7CM6BwEFCpRqPWLz?filename=guUmrEJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FguUmrEJ.jpg&h=fa09654d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然十字架山咁出名，但呢度遊客其實唔多，行左一晝都係得幾個人。行行下，見到個老師帶左一大班小朋友黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTSi81QBqSLEvh6Mip2BN3hfc89Gw7QG8qLMmkKzgxFXr?filename=WAMcykR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWAMcykR.jpg&h=d3f09e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP8E3bUaC6rBq9Qf5sB4K85VZP3uXxNCpM4q5tmEAg4jY?filename=dqKYtUc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqKYtUc.jpg&h=7cac6737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n應該係帶佢地郊遊順便認識歷史喇，呢班小朋友好活潑，不停同我地打招呼，見到男朋友拎住相機，仲自動波擺pose影相<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUc6Aknyfc7hTRS51Wu5Q5AZq8qQy2fJQHCbYRcuhE9Hg?filename=D4HWfzg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4HWfzg.jpg&h=cedbd6fc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n望左陣先知原來佢地扮緊呢度既十字架，仲識好似山上既十字架咁個個面向唔同方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />像真度極高，真係好趣緻。<br />\n<br />\n陽光燦爛既日子之下，充滿鮮花同小朋友笑聲既十字架山，感覺好有希望<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXFY1CLqP4HnEppmF8cFMU9dh1FBmmL4FNqdadgr93Ljp?filename=0zjtQ73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0zjtQ73.jpg&h=e5995b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[下一站: 立陶宛-Vilnius]<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZf6DA8pwuisaVv6rBrV8GKS2z2HNZ9xSRFnM5MTLHAB9?filename=6aSnVG8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6aSnVG8.jpg&h=c4595dca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dadee8e359611e37204438a47a8d3453592a8f4","tid":2524787,"uid":27251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T20:56:04.000Z","msg":"立陶宛妹好正，仲回味緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedbeea354d25b56bf5ffb6ba8695ee88458a335","tid":2524787,"uid":215732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T21:04:42.000Z","msg":"入左黎睇幾日 終於出新post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絲打最近點呀？ 搞咩咁夜都未訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa14c185515b5ae0091e8ea358bade51c426bd4","tid":2524787,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dadee8e359611e37204438a47a8d3453592a8f4","tid":2524787,"uid":27251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T20:56:04.000Z","msg":"立陶宛妹好正，仲回味緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T22:38:20.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"53009b20a176bf4eab1962b08c4126a119281bf3","tid":2524787,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fedbeea354d25b56bf5ffb6ba8695ee88458a335","tid":2524787,"uid":215732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T21:04:42.000Z","msg":"入左黎睇幾日 終於出