ote":{"pid":"9dadee8e359611e37204438a47a8d3453592a8f4","tid":2524787,"uid":27251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T20:56:04.000Z","msg":"立陶宛妹好正，仲回味緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T22:38:20.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-11T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"畀埋圖就自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd2dd64bae31b45b68ff454b9020713cfe240ad","tid":2524787,"uid":308262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-12T02:49:12.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">大家記得正評個po</span></span>"},{"pid":"fde8c4c3394120dba35ef75553fc1b5eb5344470","tid":2524787,"uid":64838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"新post<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af0a0821295b2f8899af2695791412c2521291c","tid":2524787,"uid":161156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53009b20a176bf4eab1962b08c4126a119281bf3","tid":2524787,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fedbeea354d25b56bf5ffb6ba8695ee88458a335","tid":2524787,"uid":215732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T21:04:42.000Z","msg":"入左黎睇幾日 終於出新post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絲打最近點呀？ 搞咩咁夜都未訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-10T22:39:05.000Z","msg":"正想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  樓主都唔後生上左年紀啦，夜訓唔會好唔舒服咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T09:51:09.000Z","msg":"還好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近排都係搵下工返下pt咁，今晚凌晨會出文架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a41d678159ce182e7ed89304e69664de4d3a1e","tid":2524787,"uid":161156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T20:16:31.000Z","msg":"[立陶宛-Vilnius]<br />\n<br />\nVilnius係立陶宛既首都，由Siauliai搭火車過去，兩個半鐘左右就去到，車廂仲非常光鮮添<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPZ1uKGdXNHymtJnYLiWU3dEbVdxoeyjjBvn5dVZnxkh9?filename=oKbsTQ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKbsTQ7.jpg&h=2cc44e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcupdu1QassFCaZRCcyeKbCBDumNgKykUkRYPPaEFjvbj?filename=W3hr9pt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW3hr9pt.jpg&h=698450ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同愛沙尼亞同拉脫維亞既首都一樣，Vilnius古城區亦係世界文化遺產，附近既屋都有返咁上下歷史，而呢種無軌電車係呢度好常見既交通工具<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma23RdgVt7oqVRA1R9WsdKQYi1Ev8Vd4eBprro7RrxnDX?filename=RKB4V5v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKB4V5v.jpg&h=37e76f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPTsHgUMBT95QmzWBKxZ1BqQMgPPh9H6pB2u89w8DCMBr?filename=udxf2Lv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fudxf2Lv.jpg&h=51804848&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n佢地既行人路燈好得意，同車用既路燈一樣，都有紅黃綠三盞燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdKJh3URg3EWGgSTEhknTkkecgZJ1a4J2iCcLuyZ4HwJA?filename=ENE6pZa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENE6pZa.jpg&h=b2a41fb5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n仲比我地搵到一樣好有親切感既野添<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWMLGzySmiDrGZGeyAcG38HRHFjvSVrD7suhwrFADMCm6?filename=1S1HHL9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1S1HHL9.jpg&h=1b693775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n殘體字既香港飯店係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />目測有好多鬼佬入去食<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcWAWqcVcEDaiGTaHMrvXnmAyzvZKthiYc4VtyTsnkRDJ?filename=kajFurc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkajFurc.jpg&h=29f756d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地對建築無乜興趣，去得多好似度度都話係世界文化遺產，間間教堂睇落都差不多咁，對於呢啲建築開始有啲審美疲勞。所以我地無特別去睇古城區，反而想繼續惡補下呢度既歷史，去左Vilnius最出名既一間博物館參觀。<br />\n<br />\nMuseum of Occupations and Freedom Fights，一間令人好難忘既博物館<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNg6tbvqXYkHxAwkxVZKoBKTzYeEEQYjvW3zKk1Pkj4gB?filename=HqjY0yZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqjY0yZ.jpg&h=71bf876e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaBFqLAyrQRLFa6XMaHLFmRRgFDEvo2bV479p7RirdWHh?filename=PZOu7d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPZOu7d2.jpg&h=c0aae5cb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcWiNAkrY2WhL4qEwzeGHkUvtvdzSj844L6WoDn5pU9eY?filename=C2kEK0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2kEK0J.jpg&h=01aaa19d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma9ACT4Eqqv3K7D3PvEQ9iBEVUX3p1NDM17zoZxkJZiqG?filename=UpAQRFK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUpAQRFK.jpg&h=3a8a6694&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n呢度既氣氛明顯比起之前Riga果間博物館沉重好多，之前果度只得展品，而呢度既地下室係侵領時期折磨同處決異見人士既監獄，有實行各種酷刑既囚室同埋處決室，成個氣氛都令人感覺好唔舒服<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXD4faS8VaghcdKanNKYgTY6Juh9FpP879AYcicHP3dHn?filename=fF9Y0AT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfF9Y0AT.jpg&h=c6ccb945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb65cyk4XUyDtPaLDgbqusm6vwcAqX6HkoY9X6RPHrx6Q?filename=8rxPnPf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rxPnPf.jpg&h=e699d132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRocTqYzZr7bsX2PBV4P4wqz9h9nKfS5ZXBnZkgU1zJtR?filename=xqE2HPg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqE2HPg.jpg&h=163d2117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n博物館名叫Museum of Occupations and Freedom Fights，除左occupation既歷史，亦有關於freedom fight既展館。入面講述左抗爭者當時點樣組織自衛隊、遊擊隊，製作既文宣，政府捉到之後受到點樣凌辱佢地、將佢地吊死係教堂門前示眾、挖眼後棄屍係街市恐嚇民眾唔好反抗。呢啲相好血淋淋，極權好可怕，更令人深深感受到立陶宛人願意犧牲自己去反抗既堅強意志。<br />\n<br />\n為左減低國內既反抗力量，除左囚禁同處決異見者，蘇聯同納粹政府仲會將人民流放至各地既集中營，迫佢地捨棄本來既國籍同宗教。即使係咁，人民既意志依然好堅定，無論去到咩地方，佢地始終堅持保留自己既傳統同語言。為左唔忘記自己既身份，佢地都會偷偷帶上一啲小物品，可能係一個小小既十字架、迷你版聖經、繡左親人名字既布碎等等。呢度展示左一啲當時佢地既隨身物品，都係立陶宛恢復獨立後由有幸生還回國既人士所捐出，其中最令我印象最深刻既係呢份15號展品<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUgJojAX5HyosBMMrRQ8iLXMA56XHQ9ttw21P574Gxypo?filename=CdtyPwa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCdtyPwa.jpg&h=359888b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢係一個火柴盒咁細既布袋，入面袋左一堆立陶宛既泥土，對物主黎講，布袋承載既唔只係泥土，仲係對故鄉呢片土地既思念同原本身分既肯定。布袋而家可以呈現我地眼前，代表最後呢個被流放既人最終都可以帶住佢回到日思夜想既家鄉，係眾多悲劇故事之中一個比較好既結局。<br />\n<br />\n每次參觀完呢啲博物館都好唔舒服，尤其是行入處決室既時候，個頭好痛好想嘔，要返出去公園啲櫈坐低抖抖氣。博物館入面紀錄左好多年青人為左奪回國家既自由獨立被迫害同殘殺，返到香港之後我都成日會諗返起，歷史果然係會不斷重演。<br />\n<br />\n慶幸既係蘇聯最終都瓦解，三小國得以重新獨立。無一個極權會係永恆，人民對自由既追求同抗爭亦係永不止息，雖然唔知黑暗會持續幾耐，但過後總會迎來光明。呢間真係一間好值得參觀既博物館。"}]}